{
  "texts": [
    "Its semantics are only latent, coincident with empirical word order.",
    "It is a flat world of one-to-one relations of tokens, where the sole difference is weighting of mutual relations across vectors.",
    "Meaningful text can only be generated by brute statistical force.",
    "The mind, by contrast, is not Bayesian.",
    "It is nothing like a neural net in the computational sense."
  ]
}